{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "49607a86-1c5e-4e3b-98a9-a232264ef951", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/49607a86-1c5e-4e3b-98a9-a232264ef951@1.pkg/1772597615866/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597616679", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/49607a86-1c5e-4e3b-98a9-a232264ef951@1.pkg/1772597615866/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597616679"}, "identifier": "49607a86-1c5e-4e3b-98a9-a232264ef951", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<p align=\"justify\">本题考查正确对待他人评价的方法。</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<p align=\"justify\">①：拒绝沟通、不采纳他人评价，违背了题干中“以人为镜”的要求，故①说法错误；</p>\n\n<p align=\"justify\">②：用心聆听并重视他人评价，是正确对待他人评价的基础，故②符合题意；</p>\n\n<p align=\"justify\">③：面对他人评价需要勇气，尤其是接受批评时，故③符合题意；</p>\n\n<p align=\"justify\">④：理性分析他人评价，避免盲从或轻视，是正确处理方式，故④符合题意；</p>\n\n<p align=\"justify\">故本题选D。</p>\n"}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<p align=\"justify\">1.（改编）《旧唐书·魏征传》中有“以人为镜，可以明得失”的千古佳句。这句话告诉我们正确对待他人的评价要（&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;）</p>\n\n<p align=\"justify\">①拒绝沟通，不采纳他人评价&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p align=\"justify\">②用心聆听，要重视他人评价</p>\n\n<p align=\"justify\">③有足够的勇气面对他人评价&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p align=\"justify\">④理性应对，不盲从也不轻视</p>\n", "title": "1.（改编）《旧唐书·魏征传》中有“以人为镜，可以明得失”的千古佳句。这句话告诉我们正确对待他人的评价要（   ）①拒绝沟通，不采纳他人评价    ②用心聆听，要重视他人评价③有足够的勇气面对他人评价    ④理性应对，不盲从也不轻视", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {"timer_type": "sequence"}, "time_dependent": false, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["D"]}], "location"